#1988-1992-1997-1998-2008
比特币的先驱。
比特币的技术不是凭空创造的，而是建立在大量研究人员的持续创新和积累。很多技术在创造时并没有产生巨大的影响，比特币将这些技术有机组合，实现了巨大的技术进步。

**密码技术：**
ECC
SHA

**共识技术：**
POW：
1992-C. Dwork and M. Naor-Pricing via processing or combatting junk mail
2004-B. Laurie and R. Clayton-Proof-of-work proves not to work
2005-J. Aspnes-Exposing computationally-challenged Byzantine impostors

**电子货币：**
ECASH：
1988-Chaum-Untraceable Electronic Cash
1999-T. Sander-Auditable, anonymous electronic cash
2001-T. Sander-Blind, auditable membership proofs

B-money:
1998-W. Dai-b-money. www.weidai.com/bmoney.txt

Bitcoin:
2008-S. Nakamoto-Bitcoin: A Peer-to-Peer Electronic Cash System. http://bitcoin.org/bitcoin.pdf

**智能合约Smart contracts**
1997-N. Szabo-Formalizing and securing relationships on public networks

